```plantuml
@startuml laziestcoder_Budget_App_JS
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "index.html" as HTML {
}

rectangle "UIController" as UIController #lightblue {
}

rectangle "budgetController" as BudgetController #lightgreen {
}

rectangle "controller" as Controller #lightgrey {
}

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> HTML : enters income/expense data

' UI Interactions
HTML --> UIController : get input values\n display budget information
UIController --> HTML : update UI with budget data

' Controller Interactions
UIController --> Controller : notify controller on user input
Controller --> BudgetController : add/delete income/expense\n calculate budget
BudgetController --> Controller : return updated budget data
Controller --> UIController : update UI with new budget

@enduml
```